---

## ğŸ§© Infrastructure Diagram
![Infrastructure](infra-diagram.png)

**Flow:**
1. Code pushed to GitHub triggers Jenkins job.  
2. Jenkins builds app, runs tests, and pushes Docker image to ECR.  
3. Terraform provisions AWS infra (VPC, EKS, RDS).  
4. Ansible deploys application on the EKS nodes.  
5. Prometheus & Grafana track metrics and alert on anomalies.

---

